'design case': the  specifies a condition when a given object has to be designed and verified; 
This value of the condition_type may be used when the Class_condition_association is referred to by a  with  'design'. 

				This value may be used to precise when a given  or a given  has to be studied by the design department so that it provides solutions appropriate for the case specified by associated_condition and associated_product_class.

'identification': the  specifies a condition that enables to distinguish the associated  from other  instances.
This value is not applicable for a top level node in a hierarchy of  instances.
This identification is part of the identification of all sub classes of this;

'design case': the  specifies a condition when a given object has to be designed and verified; 
This value of the association_type may be used when the Class_specification_association is referred to by a  with  'design'. 

				This value may be used to precise when a given  or a given  has to be studied by the design department so that it provides solutions appropriate for the case specified by the associated_specification and associated_product_class.
